		<description><![CDATA[<p><p>Feed on <a href="http://blogs.ewebpedia.com/how-to-locate-a-cell-phone/">How to Locate a Cell Phone | Track your Loved One</a> by <a href="http://blogs.ewebpedia.com">::EwebpediA BloG::</a></p><p>With the rapid development and growth in technology, our life (business or personal)&#160; has been easier to a far extend. Now, we can&#39;t think of surviving without these tech gadgets. Especially, new mobile technology and devices are invented daily. Before reading this post more, think of yourself without cell phone, laptop, tablets, ipods or simply [...]</p></p><p>Copyright © <a href="http://blogs.ewebpedia.com">::EwebpediA BloG::</a> </p>]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Feed on <a href="http://blogs.ewebpedia.com/how-to-locate-a-cell-phone/">How to Locate a Cell Phone | Track your Loved One</a> by <a href="http://blogs.ewebpedia.com">::EwebpediA BloG::</a></p><p>With the rapid development and growth in technology, our life (business or personal)&nbsp; has been easier to a far extend. Now, we can&#39;t think of surviving without these tech gadgets. Especially, new mobile technology and devices are invented daily. Before reading this post more, think of yourself without cell phone, laptop, tablets, ipods or simply internet. How does it feel to be? And yes, with the development of technology and competition in brands, almost everyone has access to certain gadget, specifically a mobile phone.&nbsp; I am also a gadget freak and try a lots of applications in different platforms. So, in this particular post, i am going to share my experience relating to navigational software and system, especially on <strong>how to locate a cell phone</strong> ,where the purpose of locating may vary among individuals.</p>
<h1><span style="font-size: 14px;">How to Loc</span><a target="_blank" href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/caseorganic/"><div id="attachment_750" class="wp-caption alignleft" style="width: 160px"><img src="../wp-content/uploads/2012/04/cell-phone-tracker-150x150.jpg" alt="how to locate a cell phone" title="cell phone tracker" class="size-thumbnail wp-image-750 wp-caption alignleft wp-caption alignleft wp-caption alignleft wp-caption alignleft wp-caption alignleft wp-caption alignleft wp-caption alignleft" height="150" width="150" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Ewebpedia &copy;--Photo Courtesy by CaseOrganic</p></div></a><span style="font-size:14px;">ate a Cell Phone:</span><span style="font-size: 14px;"> Purpose of Tracking</span></h1>
<p>Its important to know, why and where you want to use this technology. It depends on your but some common areas involve:</p>
<ul>
<li>You want to track location of your children, especially suffering from autism.</li>
<li>You want to track your lover. Reason may be different, lol.</li>
<li>You want to track your employees (From business perspective).</li>
<li>You&nbsp; want to be in touch with a group, especially your friends.</li>
<li>You want to track your lost or stolen cell phone.</li>
</ul>
<p><span id="more-749"></span></p>
<h2><span style="font-size:14px;">Apparatus Required to locate a Cell phone:</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>Smartphone (Having an operating system like iOS, andriod, symbian etc, GPS enabled preferred)</li>
<li>GPRS, 3G or wifi enabled ( internet connection should be active).</li>
<li>Application ( paid or free) properly installed to the one which you want to track.</li>
</ul>
<h3>Process:</h3>
<p>Proper application needs to be installed and must be active to the cell phone you wanna track with the minimum requirements mentioned above.</p>
<h3>Applications to track a cell phone:</h3>
<p>Now, we are in the main part and motive of this whole post and i know you are eager to get info for this. So, without taking more time, i am going to give a brief description of applications which i am using or had used for this purpose. But, you need to know that, applications vary according to operating system of mobile phones and of course some are free and most are paid.</p>
<ol>
<li><strong>Google Latitude:</strong>&#8211; As the name suggests, this is the property of Google Inc. and interestingly , it is free. It is compatible to almost mobile operating system including iOS, Nokia Smartphones, Androids, Windows Mobile 5.0+, Blackberry Smartphone etc. To install it, type <strong>http://google.com/latitude</strong> in your mobile browser, then it will automatically redirects you to proper application stores. But before using it, and due to security purposes, you need acceptance to share location from your friend or whom you want to track. Its kind of mutual sharing. It is best for group meetings and gatherings of friends. When the location is shared, it is displayed in the Google map of everyone who are allowed to view the location.<br />
<hr />
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</li>
<li><strong>Spy Bubble:&#8211;</strong>&nbsp; This is another reliable software, having a bunch of features apart of location tracking. It can track&nbsp; SMS, calls, Phone book, emails, photos etc. And yes, as like Google latitude, this works in almost Operating System. After installed once, it is hidden or undetectable which gives more security. And when you have a spybubble account, you can use it to multiple phones. This is a paid software which costs something 50$ which is less valued if we compare its features and modules. This is mostly and specifically used to spy. For more information, visit <strong><a target="_blank" href="http://www.spybubble.com/cell-phone-spy.php" target="_blank" title="More about Spybubble"><span style="color: rgb(255, 140, 0);">here</span></a></strong><br />
<hr />
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://blogs.ewebpedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/DondeEsta.png" rel="" style="" target="" title=""><div id="attachment_752" class="wp-caption alignleft" style="width: 160px"><img style="" src="http://blogs.ewebpedia.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/DondeEsta-150x150.png" alt="how to locate a cell phone" title="DondeEsta" class="size-thumbnail wp-image-752  wp-caption alignleft wp-caption alignleft wp-caption alignleft" height="150" width="150" /><p class="wp-caption-text"> Ewebpedia &copy;-- Photo by Ewebpedia Inc.</p></div></a><strong>DondeEsta SMS tracker:&#8211;&nbsp; </strong>Out of all the crowds of cell phone trackers, this may be the one which is distinct and can quench the query&nbsp; of <strong>how to locate a cell phone</strong>. With GPS functionality, it uses SMS application. All you need to do is to install it on the desired phone. After installing, you need to authorize the mobile no. ( From which you will send the query ), through this application and its done. The application will SMS your number instantly about the information of query sms you need to push so as to obtain the location. Even in active mode, it remains hidden. And the best part of this application is that, the person whom you are tracking doesn&#39;t know that he/she is being tracked, because, there are no notifications on incoming sms as well as outgoing sms embedded with his/her location. Till this date, this application is compatible with Blackberry phones, Android , Windows Mobile and Symbian but iPhone version has not been released. But, MIND&#8211; the local carrier sms tariff will be charged per sms on both the tracking and tracker mobile phones. So, check the tariffs before using it. Get it <strong><a href="http://www.dondeesta.com/rw/default.aspx" target="_blank" title="SMS location tracker"><span style="color: rgb(255, 140, 0);">here</span></a></strong><br />
<hr /></li>
<li><strong>Find my iPhone</strong>:&#8211; This is the similar software which can only be used in iOS devices like iPhone and a property of Apple Inc. To use this service, one should have an iCloud account. If you have lost your iPhone, the approximate location can be viewed in computer screen or even you can track it through another iPhone where, find my iPhone is installed. But the location services and internet connection must be active. You can even delete all data of your iPhone remotely and even can lock and put a continuous siren. Apart of this, you can send a push notification message to the thief or one who got it and can ask to return. So, this application is a must for all iPhone users.<br />
<hr />
<p>&nbsp;</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p>Ok, these are some of the popular applications (which i am using or have used) for locating or tracking cell phones. But, there may be thousands of other similar applications online. But, i do not recommend any other software which i have little or no experience.</p>
<h3>Limitation of Tracking Software:</h3>
<p>Hmmm!! I don&#39;t know how much i am successful to quench your queries via this post. But i need to mention the limitations and drawbacks of these applications. You guys might have noticed that, there are common factors or necessities for these appz to work efficiently and effectively. So, here are some limitations.</p>
<ul>
<li>Old model mobile phones are not supportive. Only Smartphones having OS, support them.</li>
<li>Internet Connection and GPS capability is the must ( exception-Google latitude works even in GPS disabled phone).</li>
<li>These apps do not work if the phone is in offline mode or switched off.</li>
<li>Location tracked and delivered may not be 100% accurate.</li>
<li>Some of these apps are expensive and may not be affordable to all.</li>
</ul>
<p>NOTE:&#8211; If you guys have any more questions and queries relating to this topic, you can ask me in the comment section. Happy Tracking!!!</p>
<p><em>[P.S. Tracking location unknowingly is restricted in some countries so, use according to the local laws with caution and for betterment]</em></p>
